Package: eurolig
Title: eurolig: Extract and analyze Euroleague basketball data
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Sergio",
           family = "Olmos Pardo",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "s.olmos.pardo@gmail.com")
Description: API wrapper around the official website of the Euroleague for easy
    extraction of basketball data. The package also provides tools to analyze 
    and visualize the data.
